  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Planck's Constant
Formula: h = 6.626×10⁻³⁴ J·s
Note:    Quantum of action; E = hf for photon energy

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   pH Definition
Formula: pH = -log[H+]
Note:    Measure of hydrogen ion concentration; 7 is neutral

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Number
Formula: e ≈ 2.71828182845...
Note:    Base of natural logarithm; fundamental to calculus

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Plate Tectonics
Formula: ~15 major plates on mantle
Note:    Explains earthquakes, volcanoes, mountain formation

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Schwarzschild Radius
Formula: r_s = 2GM/c²
Note:    Event horizon radius of a black hole

